Interface LruCacheWrapper.Delegate<K,V>

  • Enclosing class:
    LruCacheWrapper<K,V>

    public static interface LruCacheWrapper.Delegate<K,V>
    Different cache class does different work at these methods, so move them out.

    And avoid potential memory leak which may occur if making ExtendedLruCache an inner class.
